<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<%= render :partial => 'layouts/head_tags' %>
	<body id="homepage">
    <header id="homepage-top">
      <nav class="navbar navbar-default" role="navigation">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="navbar-header">
            <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#bs-example-navbar-collapse-1">
              <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
              <span class="icon-bar"></span>
              <span class="icon-bar"></span>
              <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="bs-example-navbar-collapse-1">
            <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
            	<li><%= link_to "home", root_path %></li>
              <li><%= link_to "about mi", about_path %></li>
              <li><%= link_to "contact", contact_path %></li>
              <% if current_user %>
                  <li><%= link_to "my inventories", inspections_path %></li>
                	<li><%= link_to "profile", profile_path %></li>
                  <li><%= link_to 'sign out', signout_path, method: "delete" %></li>
              <% else %>
              	<li><%= link_to "get started", signup_path %></li>
                <li><%= link_to "sign in", signin_path %></li>
              <% end %>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </nav>
      <%= image_tag 'mi_logo_white.png', class: 'hompage_logo' %>
    </header>
    <section id="homepage-tagline">
      <div class="container">
        <div id="why-mi">
          <p class="tagline-title">Why do you need MyInventory?</p>
          <p class="tagline-body">
            You never know when a disaster may strike, a burglar might occur, but you can be prepared with a room by room inventory of all your personal possessions. Of course one can simply make a list of items and save receipts in a file but when a disaster occurs where is this list when you need it. With our 24/7 on line system your personal inventory is always there with a click of your mouse. 
          </p>
          <p class="tagline-body">
          Having up to date inventory will help you get your insurance claim settled fasterâ€¦help you make a wise decision on how much insurance is enough to replace all your personal things, and substantiate losses for your income tax return.
          </p>
          <p class="tagline-body">
            Did you know that jewelry, furs, collectibles and expensive items may need separate insurance.
          </p>
          
          <p class="tagline-body">
          Our system makes taking pictures/videos easy better yet we offer in home personal consulting through one of our insured personal agents that will make this task even simpler buy doing the inventory for you.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="homepage-main">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-3 homepage-block">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-cloud" style="font-size:12em"></span>
            <p class="head">Cloud Based<p>
            <p class="body">MyInventory reports are created online. You don't need to download software and it doesn't take a degree to learn how to use it.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3 homepage-block">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-lock" style="font-size:10em;"></span>
            <p class="head">Secure<p>
            <p class="body">MyInventory is a safe and secure website. We do all we can to protect your account and maintain your privacy.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3 homepage-block">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-envelope" style="font-size:10em;"></span>
            <p class="head">Share<p>
            <p class="body">Reports can easily be emailed from within the MyInventory software. Recipients can view online or print their own personal copy.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3 homepage-block">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-folder-close" style="font-size:10em;"></span>
            <p class="head">Online Storage<p>
            <p class="body">You inventory is stored online. Access it from any device, anywhere, any time you need it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <footer>
    	<div class="container">
      	<small>&copy; 2014 - MyInventory - All Rights Reserved. <%= link_to 'Terms & Conditions', toc_path %></small>
    	</div>
    </footer>
	</body>
</html>